#compdef picoprobe
# Documentation: https://github.com/raspberrypi/debugprobe
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-17
# Verified: raspberrypi/debugprobe upstream (renamed from
# picoprobe). NOTE: picoprobe is FIRMWARE (UF2 file flashed to
# an RP2040), NOT a CLI binary. End users interact with the probe
# via `openocd -f interface/cmsis-dap.cfg` (modern) or
# `interface/picoprobe.cfg` (legacy), and via `picotool` for
# flashing. This completion exists for compat with shells that
# expect a stub.
# Removed from prior file: bogus man.archlinux.org search URL;
# fabricated -h/-v (picoprobe is not a callable binary).

local ret=1
_message 'picoprobe is firmware (UF2), not a CLI; use openocd or picotool instead' && ret=0
return ret
